# Catch-all for dot-prefix scratch .txt files at the repo root (SSH
# output captures via the two-step Windows pattern, ad-hoc diagnostics,
# debug artifacts). 2026-05-06 audit cleanup — replaces the per-prefix
# lines above for any future diagnostic session. Anchored with leading
# / so subdir test fixtures (e.g. tests/fixtures/.golden_output.txt) are
# NOT silently ignored.
/.[A-Za-z]*.txt
